text: Reynaldo Villar Umali (February 26, 1957 â€“ January 7, 2021) was a Filipino politician. He was a member of the House of Representatives of the Philippines from 2010 to 2019. He ran for governor of Oriental Mindoro in 2019 but lost to Humerlito Dolor.
